  "text": "When social bias for a direct inquiry of WTP is considered (c.f. Sect. 2.4.4), the actual WTP would lie 1.5-3 times lower (List and Gallet 2001; [CITATION_1] . Thus, a price of as low as 0.4% of the price of a middle class limousine (=worst case: 1.3%/3) or as high as 1.1% (=best case: 1.7%/1.5) should be aimed for.",
